Package: EpigeneticAgePipeline
Type: Package
Title: Package designed for processing and analyzing DNA methylation data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Stanislav", 
    "Rayevskiy", 
    email = "srayevsk@uwo.ca", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID="0009-0005-2942-5939"))
biocViews: DNAMethylation, Epigenetics, MethylationArray, Normalization, 
    PrincipalComponent
Description: EpigeneticAgePipeline is a comprehensive package designed 
    for processing and analyzing DNA methylation data.
    The package provides a variety of epigenetic age measures,
    epigenetic age acceleration measures, residual generation, 
    and cell-count generation.
    The package also provides a set of 
    plots and tables used for further analysis.
